            {
              "enText": "<b>Lesson 1 • Talking about a new project</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "Carl, Greg and Anne work for WaterSonic Corporation. Recently, the company has come up with an idea for a new electric toothbrush."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Carl:</b> I think we've <b>come up with a winner</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Anne:</b> I agree. The new Brush-o-matic should be a <b>blockbuster</b>!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Carl:</b> Our designers have already made up some prototypes. The toothbrushes have a tooth-whitening attachment and many other <b>bells and whistles</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Greg:</b> We should <b>fast track a project</b>. Let's try to launch it in time for the holiday season."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Anne:</b> This will be a great <b>stocking stuffer</b>!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Carl:</b> We definitely need a <b>big win</b> for the holidays."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Anne:</b> This is a great idea. We're going to <b>make a killing</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Greg:</b> Let's not talk about this project to anybody who doesn't need to know. We'll <b>keep something under wraps</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Carl:</b> I agree <b>mum's the word</b>. We don't want any of our competitors to <b>get wind of</b> the idea and <b>rip it off</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Anne:</b> Right. Let's meet again on Monday morning and discuss our <b>game plan</b> for <b>getting this project off the ground</b>!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
